precis:
Enactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN
LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (Tombstone Territorial Park Reservation,
Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of specified
tracts of land in the Yukon, until December 31, 2004, and (b) the repeal of
Order in Council P.C. 1999-2227.
